  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Financial Analyst (Manufacturing Costs)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a leading manufacturing company in precision engineering industry. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting an Cost Analyst to be part of their FP&A Team. They are located in the West - easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Duties of Cost Analyst:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform monthly actual vs. standard cost variance analysis.</li><li>Analyze material, labor, and overhead variances and work with cross-functional teams to identify root causes.</li><li>Monitor production cost trends and manufacturing/inventory KPIs.</li><li>Identify key cost drivers and risks impacting gross profit.</li><li>Ensure accurate inventory valuation and proper cost flow through COGS.</li><li>Manage manufacturing variances and support regular standard cost reviews.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in accounting field</li><li>Min 3 years of costing analysis experience in manufacturing industry</li><li>Able to work in fast-paced environment</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</li></ul>",
